The '''EPT-212''' was a security device manufactured by [[Fabritech/Legends|Fabritech]]. The device scanned for frequencies specific to [[Droid/Legends|droid]] wireless systems and droid [[Power cell/Legends|power cell]] oscillations.

[[Chalmun/Legends|Chalmun]] installed a refurbished EPT-212 in his [[Mos Eisley/Legends|Mos Eisley]] [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Cantina]] to discourage droids from entering the premises. At some point it was stolen by [[Dathcha/Legends|Dathcha]], but soon returned by a local [[Spacer/Legends|spacer]].

